    <item>
      <title>美联储告诉银行不要羞于向其要钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/fed-aims-to-end-discount-window-stigma-for-banks-who-borrow-from-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当 Brookline Bancorp Inc. 需要快速借入短期现金时——这是这家总部位于波士顿的贷方日常业务的一部分——它有一系列的选择。然而，它不愿求助的廉价资金来源之一是美联储，因为担心会敲响警钟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/fed-aims-to-end-discount-window-stigma-for-banks-who-borrow-from-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“小白鼠”赞比亚警告称，如果二十国集团债务减免失败，将会发生灾难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/-guinea-pig-zambia-warns-of-disaster-if-g-20-debt-relief-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚总统哈坎德·希奇莱马表示，赞比亚是二十国集团计划的“实验品”，该计划旨在帮助贫穷国家重组无力承担的债务，如果无法赢得救济，对其他需要帮助的国家来说将意味着灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/-guinea-pig-zambia-warns-of-disaster-if-g-20-debt-relief-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 10:53:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将于一月前列出符合资助资格的房地产项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/china-to-list-property-projects-eligible-for-funding-by-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国住建部门将于一月底公布第一批符合资助资格的项目清单，以支持开发商并遏制中国房地产市场放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/china-to-list-property-projects-eligible-for-funding-by-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 08:41:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Otedola 帮助亿万富翁 Aliko Dangote 的财富升至十年来最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/nigerian-tycoon-dangote-s-wealth-at-22-billion-as-otedola-buys-cement-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚大亨费米·奥特多拉 (Femi Otedola) 表示，他将增购丹格特水泥公司 (Dangote Cement Plc) 的股票，因为他最近的收购在一定程度上帮助推动了水泥制造商亿万富翁阿利科·丹格特 (Aliko Dangote) 的财富达到十年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/nigerian-tycoon-dangote-s-wealth-at-22-billion-as-otedola-buys-cement-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 06:32:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受冲突和刺激因素影响，油价将录得数月来最大单周涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[浸油——但仍有望创下 10 月份以来的最大单周涨幅——美国库存下降以及中国政府推出更多刺激措施的前景帮助推动原油价格突破近期区间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 00:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
